Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.00,0:09:01.45,OP II BR,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCFE052&}ninguém responde. Tudo desapareceu no vazio!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.41,0:09:06.24,OP II BR,,0,0,0,,Por ora, libertem-se! Libertem-se! Continuem!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.24,0:09:12.65,OP II BR,,0,0,0,,Chorem! Chorem! Mantenham sua determinação no alto!
